00:01.413 --> 00:02.981
- Excuse me, hey!
- I'm sorry.

00:03.115 --> 00:05.404
- Is this your trash?
- I'm overseeing the renovation.

00:05.483 --> 00:07.651
- So yeah, I guess it is.
- Okay if I take this?

00:07.685 --> 00:09.286
Misdemeanor, attempted extortion...

00:09.320 --> 00:12.456
I never saw this coming. Not from you.

00:12.490 --> 00:13.707
John hates me.

00:13.741 --> 00:16.560
You guys had a really
good relationship before.

00:16.594 --> 00:19.629
You need to find a way to remind him.

00:19.664 --> 00:21.565
I don't want to play with you scrubs.

00:21.599 --> 00:23.333
Fine. You don't want to play field hockey.

00:23.367 --> 00:24.568
How about basketball? If I win,

00:24.602 --> 00:25.752
then you've gotta join the team.

00:25.803 --> 00:27.537
I win, you drive me to
school every morning.

00:29.674 --> 00:31.541
See you at 7:00.

00:31.576 --> 00:32.642
You're here to play.

00:32.677 --> 00:34.644
If she's the best player you've got,

00:34.679 --> 00:35.745
you're going to need me.

00:35.780 --> 00:37.681
