36:19.686 --> 36:22.571
Hey, I got your message.

36:22.605 --> 36:24.523
Thanks for coming in.

36:24.557 --> 36:27.326
I thought I should follow
up after that odd experience

36:27.360 --> 36:29.294
you must have had.

36:29.329 --> 36:31.663
It's fine.

36:31.698 --> 36:34.299
Stop saying it's fine when it isn't.

36:34.334 --> 36:37.402
I mean, it's like the question thing.

36:37.437 --> 36:39.705
We fought so hard so you
wouldn't have to do it,

36:39.739 --> 36:42.741
and you girls just keep doing it.

36:42.775 --> 36:45.544
I'm sorry.

36:45.578 --> 36:46.778
I'm sorry for saying sorry.

36:46.813 --> 36:51.517
Mm. Look, clearly, I'm not
in a great place right now.

36:51.551 --> 36:55.320
So just forget everything I said.

36:55.355 --> 36:57.322
Go and have fun at art school.

36:57.357 --> 37:00.659
Fall in love. Get your heart broken.

37:00.693 --> 37:03.262
Do derivative stuff.

37:03.296 --> 37:05.280
Do beautiful stuff that
you never even thought

37:05.315 --> 37:06.398
you had in you.

37:07.767 --> 37:10.285
Here's my letter.

37:10.320 --> 37:12.321
Thank you.

37:12.372 --> 37:14.406
But I don't think I'm
going to send a letter

37:14.440 --> 37:16.308
of recommendation in with my application.

37:16.342 --> 37:18.410
I'm just going to submit my work,

37:18.444 --> 37:19.545
let it speak for itself,

37:19.579 --> 37:21.547
and if they don't like it then screw 'em.

37:21.581 --> 37:23.448
Ballsy move.

37:23.483 --> 37:26.318
Well, you're at your best when
you don't give a crap, right?

37:26.352 --> 37:27.686
You know what...

37:27.720 --> 37:29.588
I love it.

37:29.622 --> 37:32.658
But save the Patti
Smith stuff for the work.

37:32.692 --> 37:34.693
Trust me on this one.

37:34.727 --> 37:36.345
Take the letter.

37:36.396 --> 37:38.297
Okay, good call.

37:48.374 --> 37:49.708
Can I help you?

37:51.411 --> 37:52.678
According to my assistant,

37:52.712 --> 37:55.547
I was a bit of a sociopath yesterday.

37:55.582 --> 37:58.417
So she bought me some flowers.

37:58.451 --> 38:02.621
Look, I'm not great with people.

38:02.655 --> 38:04.323
But I'm smart, I pay well,

38:04.357 --> 38:05.657
and I know talent when I see it.

38:05.692 --> 38:09.461
You basically told me

38:09.495 --> 38:11.296
if I wasn't ready to ditch my kids,

38:11.331 --> 38:12.631
I'd be doomed to kitchen makeovers.

38:12.665 --> 38:14.266
I didn't say ditch your kids.

38:14.300 --> 38:15.500
I got kids.

38:15.535 --> 38:18.437
Look, forget what I said.

38:18.471 --> 38:20.439
I knew you were the
perfect person for the job,

38:20.473 --> 38:22.274
and I lost my head.

38:22.308 --> 38:24.276
What do you care?

38:24.310 --> 38:26.445
All you liked was one stupid lamp.

38:27.680 --> 38:31.383
Because I hate it when
people make asinine decisions.

38:31.417 --> 38:33.452
And this is your attempt to win me back?

38:33.486 --> 38:35.353
This is me giving you a lifeline.

38:35.371 --> 38:37.623
I mean, are you so...

38:41.494 --> 38:43.362
I have some local projects.

38:43.396 --> 38:45.764
I'd like to find something
for you to work on

38:45.798 --> 38:49.534
so you can tuck your giant
teenagers in at night.

38:49.569 --> 38:51.470
This whole thing of insulting people

38:51.504 --> 38:53.505
to motivate them... that
does not work for me.

38:53.539 --> 38:55.407
I'm passionate.

38:55.441 --> 38:57.509
I can't promise I'm not
going to yell at you.

38:57.543 --> 38:59.611
I can't promise I'm not going to yell back.

38:59.646 --> 39:02.280
Works for me.

39:04.584 --> 39:07.269
Okay.

39:10.523 --> 39:12.607
Thanks.

39:51.430 --> 39:52.597
Hi.

39:52.615 --> 39:53.699
Oh, hey.

39:57.637 --> 39:59.504
Thanks.

40:00.773 --> 40:03.542
I...

40:06.546 --> 40:08.714
I'm way too hard on you.

40:08.748 --> 40:10.549
It's okay.

40:10.583 --> 40:12.517
No, it's not okay.

40:12.552 --> 40:14.319
You see...

40:14.353 --> 40:16.354
Sometimes I feel like

40:16.389 --> 40:18.423
I have to cram

40:18.458 --> 40:22.728
16 years of parenting

40:22.762 --> 40:26.531
into the few years that
you're actually around.

40:26.566 --> 40:28.366
And the truth is,

40:28.401 --> 40:31.703
you were just fine before I came along.

40:34.807 --> 40:37.809
I never thought that I'd
have to say this to you,

40:37.827 --> 40:41.379
but this... all this...

40:41.414 --> 40:44.349
is your home.

40:44.383 --> 40:46.485
And it always will be.

40:46.519 --> 40:49.721
Even if I rob a few banks?

40:49.756 --> 40:53.291
Even if.

41:05.337 --> 41:06.638
What the hell is this?

41:07.707 --> 41:09.441
I mean, come on!

41:09.475 --> 41:12.444
- Round, flat...
- It's hard.

41:12.478 --> 41:14.446
This makes no sense to me whatsoever.

41:14.480 --> 41:15.514
They don't make it easy.

41:15.548 --> 41:17.415
No. No, here here. Here, show me.

41:17.450 --> 41:18.583
Show me, show me.

41:18.618 --> 41:20.452
Whoo!

41:20.486 --> 41:21.753
- You choke up on it.
- Yeah.

